title: Dirt Devil Power Duo™ Carpet and Hard Floor Cyclonic Upright: How to Use
description: Here’s how to use the Power Duo Carpet + Hard Floor Cyclonic Vacuum (UD20125B)  to clean your entire home.

asset.author: Dirt Devil
asset.hookText: Here’s how to use the Power Duo Carpet + Hard Floor Cyclonic Vacuum (UD20125B)  to clean your entire home.

transcripts: Really easy to clean your whole home. First step on the nozzle and pull back to recline. Push here and you're ready to vacuum your carpets for above floor messes. Press the release button and pull the wand out now push your extension on to the end for cleaning hard to reach areas. Use the crevice tool to get the small stuff in cracks corners and couches. Push the brush until it clicks for dusting shelves and tables. Push down to switch it back the back at the same time and it has flexible edges up against baseboards when you're done. Toss the washer into the washer so it's ready for next time.
